Use `detect_languages()` from `fs.py` and project-specific detection:

```python
# ✅ GOOD
language_counts = detect_languages(repo_dir)
if "JavaScript" in language_counts or "TypeScript" in language_counts:
    # Run Node audit

# ✅ GOOD
if has_node_project(repo_dir):  # Checks for package.json
